00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:34,340
have arrived with a camera eye essentially independently.

794
00:43:34,340 --> 00:43:35,340
It's convergent evolution.

795
00:43:35,340 --> 00:43:38,340
They started from a light sensitive spot,

796
00:43:38,340 --> 00:43:42,340
and independently they ended up with a camera type eye.

797
00:43:42,340 --> 00:43:45,340
There are one or two regulatory genes in common,

